    <data key="d0">TASOLS Event-Driven Serverless Machine Learning Pipeline</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GJ1So_pbZWk</data>
    <data key="d2">A serverless, event-driven machine learning architecture that chains SageMaker models (k-means clustering and random forest prediction) to deliver real-time recommendations and BI dashboards.</data>
